c: 10
v: 107
t: "Sano Allah naga ali atite ankwayikasye masausyo, basi pangali ŵampaka agakungunukule ikaŵeje Jwalakwe, soni naga ansachilile yambone, basi pangali jwampaka awuwusye ukoto Wakwe, akuwuyikasyaga kwa jwansachile mwa achikapolo Ŵakwe, soni Jwalakwe ni Jwakululuka kusyene, Jwachanasa channope"